headline: Heard on the Street Thursday Recap: Memory Boost
summary: Technology stocks led indexes higher. Megacap techs made a strong comeback from Wednesday's selloff. The Nasdaq composite gained 1.4%, while the S&P 500 rose 0.8%. Government data indicated inflation is cooling.
